<bibRefCitation id="EFE29EF0227BFFAEAAEB1094FB5FAB26" author="Kazerani, F. &amp; Talebi, A. A. &amp; Gilasian, E." box="[974,1221,239,266]" pageId="2" pageNumber="243" pagination="287 - 291" refId="ref4362" refString="Kazerani, F., Talebi, A. A. &amp; Gilasian, E. 2012. First record of the genus and species Pipiza accola Violovitsh (Diptera: Syrphidae) from Iran. Journal of Crop Protection, 1 (4), 287 - 291." type="journal article" year="2012">Kazerani et al., 2012</bibRefCitation>
